<record>
<name>charming</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>medium</power>
<value>7500</value>
<aura>faint enchantment</aura>
<align>CLNGE</align>
<hint>enchanting creature</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>When played this %Item% enables the performer to work one suggestion (as the spell, Will DC 14 negates) into the music for each 10 minutes of playing if %GenderSub% can succeed on a DC 14 Perform (musical instruments) check. If the check fails, the audience cannot be affected by any further performances from the player for 24 hours.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>clear thought</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>medium</power>
