<record>
<name>disguise</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>minor</power>
<value>1800</value>
<aura>faint illusion</aura>
<align>CNE</align>
<hint>nil</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>This piece of %Type% allows the owner to alter her appearance as with a disguise self spell. As part of the disguise, the %Item% can be altered to look unassuming or quite extravagant.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>displacement</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>medium</power>
<value>24000</value>
<aura>faint illusion</aura>
<align>CNE</align>
<hint>shadow</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>This item appears to be a normal %Item%, but when worn by a character its magical properties distort and warp light waves. This displacement works similar to the displacement spell except that it only grants a 20 percent miss chance on attacks against the wearer. It functions continually.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>displacement</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>major</power>
<value>50000</value>
<aura>moderate illusion</aura>
<align>CNE</align>
<hint>shadow</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>This item appears to be a normal %Item%, but on command its magical properties distort and warp light waves. This displacement works just like the displacement spell and lasts for a total of 15 rounds per day, which the wearer can divide up as %GenderSub% sees fit.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>doom</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>medium</power>
<value>25000</value>
<aura>moderate necromancy</aura>
<align>NE</align>
<hint>evil outsider</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>The {Cap~%Item%} of Doom, when %Use%, enables the character to cast doom upon those around %GenderObj% (one target per round) as a gaze attack, but as a standard action. Those merely looking at the character are not affected. Those failing a DC 11 Will save are affected as by the doom spell. Additionally the owner of the %Item% has a continual deathwatch effect and can use fear (Will DC 16 partial) as a normal gaze attack once per week. The user's eyes will momentarily glow red when the doom or fear power is used.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>dwarvenkind</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>medium</power>
<value>14900</value>
<aura>moderate divination</aura>
<align>CLNGE</align>
<hint>dwarf</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>This %Item% gives the user a +4 competence bonus on Charisma checks and Charisma based skill checks as they relate to dealing with dwarves, a +2 competence bonus on similar checks when dealing with gnomes and halflings, and a -2 competence penalty on similar checks when dealing with anyone else. The wearer can understand, speak, and read Dwarven. If the wearer is not a dwarf, %GenderSub% gains 60-foot darkvision, dwarven stonecunning, a +2 enhancement bonus to Constitution, and a +2 resistance bonus on saves against poison, spells, or spell-like effects. *These bonus should be added to the character as required by the encounter*</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>eagle</name>
<probability>1</probability>
