<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>This seemingly normal %Item% is a potent aid to all spellcasters who prepare spells (clerics, druids, rangers, paladins, and wizards). Once per day on command, a {Cap~%Item%} of Power enables the possessor to recall any one spell that %GenderSub% had prepared and then cast. The spell is then prepared again, just as if it had not been cast. The spell must be of 1st level. It can only be used once per day.</dmdescrip>
</record>
