<dmdescrip>This finely cut %Item% is indistinguishable from an ordinary jewel in appearance. When it is gazed through, the %Item% of seeing enables the user to see as though %GenderSub% were affected by the true seeing spell. A {Cap~%Item%} of Seeing can be used for as much as 30 minutes a day, divided up into periods of minutes or rounds as the user sees fit.</dmdescrip>
