<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>This normal-seeming %Item% if clasped firmly in hand or held to the breast while the possessor attempts actions related to the %Item%'s powers, %GenderSub% understands and is able to employ the item. The %Item% enables its possessor to breathe in water as if %GenderSub% were in clean, fresh air. {Cap~%GenderSub%} swim speed is 60 feet, and %GenderSub% can cast spells and act underwater without hindrance.</dmdescrip>
</record>
