<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>When worn, the %Item% enables movement on vertical surfaces or even upside down along ceilings at a speed of 20, leaving the wearer's hands free. The %Item% will not grant spider climbing on severely slippery surfaces-icy, oiled, or greased surfaces. The %Item% can be used for 10 minutes per day, split up as the wearer chooses.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>storms</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>major</power>
<value>48000</value>
<aura>various</aura>
<align>CLNGE</align>
<hint>nil</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>The possessor of the {Cap~%Item%} of Storms can call forth all manner of weather, even supernaturally destructive storms. Once per day %GenderSub% can call upon the orb to use a control weather spell, Once per month, %GenderSub% can conjure a storm of vengeance. The possessor of the %Item% is continually protected by an endure elements effect.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>swimming and climbing</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>minor</power>
<value>6250</value>
