<hint>nil</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>The {Cap~%Item%} of Swimming and Climbing grant a +5 competence bonus on Swim checks and Climb checks.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>telepathy</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>medium</power>
<value>27000</value>
<aura>faint divination</aura>
<align>CLNGE</align>
<hint>nil</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>The wearer can use detect thoughts at will. Furthermore, %GenderSub% can send a telepathic message to anyone whose surface thoughts %GenderSub% is reading (allowing two-way communication). Once per day, the wearer of the %Item% can implant a suggestion (as the spell, Will DC 14 negates) along with his telepathic message.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>teleportation</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>major</power>
<value>73500</value>
<aura>moderate conjuration</aura>
<align>CLNGE</align>
<hint>nil</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>A character wearing the %Item% may teleport three times per day, exactly as if %GenderSub% had cast the spell of the same name.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
