<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>This appears to be a normal %Item%. The %Item% allows the wearer to read the thoughts of others, as with the spell detect thoughts.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>undead turning</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>medium</power>
<value>11000</value>
<aura>moderate necromancy</aura>
<align>CLNGE</align>
<hint>nil</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>This %Item% is a boon to any character able to turn undead, allowing %GenderObj% to do so as if his class level were four levels higher than it actually is.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
<name>undeadbane</name>
<probability>1</probability>
<power>minor</power>
<value>2500</value>
<aura>moderate divination</aura>
<align>CLNGE</align>
<hint>nil</hint>
<modify>nil</modify>
<roll>nil</roll>
<bonus>nil</bonus>
<dmdescrip>This %Item% allows its user to detect any undead within 60 feet, although %GenderSub% must concentrate (a standard action) in order for the detection to take place. The %Item% also enables its possessor to combat undead with weapons, unarmed attacks, or natural weapons as if the undead had no damage reduction.</dmdescrip>
</record>
<record>
